---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout lang="en" title="Social Media Templates | 1hcrypto" description="Twitter/X and Telegram content templates for daily market analysis and trade signals.">
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-2">📱 Social Media Templates</h1>
    <p class="text-[var(--text-muted)] mb-10">Copy-paste ready. Post daily at 08:30 Beijing Time.</p>

    <!-- Twitter/X Templates -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="text-2xl">🐦</span> Twitter/X Templates
      </h2>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-[var(--bg-secondary)] border border-[var(--border-color)]">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
            <span class="text-xs font-mono text-primary bg-primary/10 px-2 py-1 rounded">Daily Analysis</span>
            <button onclick="navigator.clipboard.writeText(this.closest('.p-6').querySelector('pre').textContent)" class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)] hover:text-primary transition-colors">Copy</button>
          </div>
          <pre class="text-sm text-[var(--text-primary)] whitespace-pre-wrap font-sans leading-relaxed bg-[var(--bg-card)] p-4 rounded-lg overflow-x-auto">📊 BTC Daily Analysis (2026-05-31)

1H Close: 71,200
Key Levels:
• Support: 70,500 / 69,800
• Resistance: 72,000 / 73,500

Signal: 1H EMA20 crossing up, RSI 58, funding -0.003% (shorts pay)

Bias: Bullish. Wait for pullback to 70,500 to long. SL 69,700.

Full analysis: https://1hcrypto.com/en/daily/2026-05-31/

#BTC #Crypto #TechnicalAnalysis</pre>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-[var(--bg-secondary)] border border-[var(--border-color)]">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
            <span class="text-xs font-mono text-amber-500 bg-amber-500/10 px-2 py-1 rounded">Trade Alert</span>
            <button onclick="navigator.clipboard.writeText(this.closest('.p-6').querySelector('pre').textContent)" class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)] hover:text-primary transition-colors">Copy</button>
          </div>
          <pre class="text-sm text-[var(--text-primary)] whitespace-pre-wrap font-sans leading-relaxed bg-[var(--bg-card)] p-4 rounded-lg overflow-x-auto">⚡ Paper Trade Update

📈 Opened: BTC/USDT Long
Entry: 71,200
SL: 70,400
TP: 73,000 (1:2.25 R:R)

Reason: 1H breakout + negative funding + OI rising

Analysis: https://1hcrypto.com/en/daily/2026-05-31/

⚠️ Paper trading only — not investment advice

#BTC #Trading</pre>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-[var(--bg-secondary)] border border-[var(--border-color)]">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
            <span class="text-xs font-mono text-green-500 bg-green-500/10 px-2 py-1 rounded">Weekly Recap</span>
            <button onclick="navigator.clipboard.writeText(this.closest('.p-6').querySelector('pre').textContent)" class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)] hover:text-primary transition-colors">Copy</button>
          </div>
          <pre class="text-sm text-[var(--text-primary)] whitespace-pre-wrap font-sans leading-relaxed bg-[var(--bg-card)] p-4 rounded-lg overflow-x-auto">📅 Weekly Recap (May 26-30)

BTC: +3.2%, weekly close bullish
ETH: +5.1%, outperforming BTC
Accuracy: 12/18 = 66.7%

Next week key levels:
• BTC support 69,500, resistance 73,000
• ETH support 3,600, resistance 3,900

Full recap: https://1hcrypto.com/en/weekly/

#Crypto #WeeklyRecap</pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Telegram Templates -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="text-2xl">✈️</span> Telegram Templates
      </h2>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-[var(--bg-secondary)] border border-[var(--border-color)]">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
            <span class="text-xs font-mono text-primary bg-primary/10 px-2 py-1 rounded">Channel Daily Post</span>
            <button onclick="navigator.clipboard.writeText(this.closest('.p-6').querySelector('pre').textContent)" class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)] hover:text-primary transition-colors">Copy</button>
          </div>
          <pre class="text-sm text-[var(--text-primary)] whitespace-pre-wrap font-sans leading-relaxed bg-[var(--bg-card)] p-4 rounded-lg overflow-x-auto">📊 【Daily Analysis】2026-05-31

BTC/USDT 1H Analysis

💰 Current Price: 71,200
📍 Support: 70,500 / 69,800
📍 Resistance: 72,000 / 73,500

📈 Technical:
• EMA20: 71,000 (price above, bullish)
• RSI: 58 (healthy bullish zone)
• Funding: -0.003% (shorts pay, bullish signal)
• OI: +2.1% (capital flowing in)

✅ Trade Idea: Wait for pullback to 70,500 to long. SL 69,700, TP 73,000

📖 Full analysis: https://1hcrypto.com/en/daily/2026-05-31/

⚠️ For reference only — not investment advice</pre>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-[var(--bg-secondary)] border border-[var(--border-color)]">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
            <span class="text-xs font-mono text-red-500 bg-red-500/10 px-2 py-1 rounded">Market Alert</span>
            <button onclick="navigator.clipboard.writeText(this.closest('.p-6').querySelector('pre').textContent)" class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)] hover:text-primary transition-colors">Copy</button>
          </div>
          <pre class="text-sm text-[var(--text-primary)] whitespace-pre-wrap font-sans leading-relaxed bg-[var(--bg-card)] p-4 rounded-lg overflow-x-auto">🚨 【Market Alert】

BTC 1H big red candle, broke below 70,800 support.

📉 Current: 70,600 (-1.8%)
📊 Volume: Significantly above average
💧 Liquidation: ~$12M longs wiped

👀 Watching:
• Whether 70,500 holds (key support)
• If broken, next support 69,800
• Whether volume continues expanding

📖 Live updates: https://1hcrypto.com/en/daily/2026-05-31/

⚠️ For reference only</pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-[var(--bg-card)] border border-[var(--border-color)]">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-4">📋 Usage Guide</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)]">
        <li>✅ Post daily analysis template at 08:30 Beijing Time</li>
        <li>✅ Post trade alert within 5 mins of opening a position</li>
        <li>✅ Post result update after SL/TP is triggered</li>
        <li>✅ Post weekly recap template after weekly review is published</li>
        <li>⚠️ Always keep the disclaimer — do not remove</li>
        <li>⚠️ Links must point to the specific analysis page, not the homepage</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
